title: [dogfooding] [BLOCKER] Application crashes on open - MacBook
body:
# Bug Report

## Description

I install the application on my MacBook, I attempt to open the application, the application crashes.

I have tried many times with uninstalling and restarting at every stage of the process. I've manually and painstakingly removed all files and directories related to the status installation and then restarted, then I've reinstalled and restarted, then opened the application only for it to crash immediately.

Logs provided below:

## Steps to reproduce

Install desktop application on my MacBook
Open application
Crashes

#### Expected behavior

The application opens

#### Actual behavior

The application does not open

### Additional Information

- Status desktop version: 0.7.0
- Operating System: MacOS Big Sur version 11.6
